ComicInfo.Summary: The last 16 of the exclusive WildGuard Internet comic strips are presented in the conclusion of this miniseries. Also this issue, Snapback recalls the day he told two of his fellow Tri-County Power Patrol members he was auditioning for WildGuard. The 'Where Are They Now?' feature spotlights rejected contenders, Strong-Bot and Running Girl.
ComicInfo.Title: Audition Tapes; Messages; Expectations
